  SHEPPARD
     (with deeper voice, into Genii radio) Huron here.

  TERAN
     (over radio) What's your status.

  SHEPPARD
     (with deep voice, into radio) Good.

  TERAN
     (over radio) Elaborate.

  SHEPPARD
     (with deep voice, into radio) Real good.

  HURON
     (crying out) Help us!

  GENII SCIENTIST
     Help us!

