LOCATION--FOREST, DAY

  ANNOTATION
     The Genii run towards the ruins.


LOCATION--TEMPLE OF LAROS RUINS, DAY

  ANNOTATION
     McKay works on the crystal control panel.

  MCKAY
     (calling to Sheppard) You know, you're not exactly
