  SHEPPARD
     More than seven?

  MCKAY
     Try seven thousand!

  SHEPPARD
     Well, that's less than infinite.

  ANNOTATION
     McKay's scanner beeps, and he sighs in
     frustration.

  SHEPPARD
     (to Harmony) All right, look. It's going to get
